7Ô∏è‚É£ Can constructors have access modifiers?

public  - normal object creation
private - singleton
protected - factory pattern
default - package control


üîüAccess modifiers vs Spring annotations (üî• TRICKY)
‚ùì Can Spring autowire private fields/methods?

@Autowired
private OrderService orderService;
‚úÖ YES
why?
spring usese reflection, not java access rules

java access modifier apply at compile time, 
spring works at run time using reflections

üîüWhy are entity fields usually private?

@Entity
class User{
  private String name;
}
Reason:
    encapsulation
    Validation via setters
    Hibernate use reflections

Expose data via DTOs, not entities.



